{"tid":2337453,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"檢查染疫者喉嚨肺部  戴齊口罩面罩 西醫仍中招","createTime":"2020-12-23T09:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T10:56:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff652176760916bcf12da2fcc60737c0c0b83c2","tid":2337453,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T09:57:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/F73ZJK3NJFCP5B5WNQOSNGTHAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2FF73ZJK3NJFCP5B5WNQOSNGTHAU%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp7ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=6cd13676\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2FF73ZJK3NJFCP5B5WNQOSNGTHAU%2F&h=7fcca263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/F73ZJK3NJFCP5B5WNQOSNGTHAU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n檢查染疫者喉嚨肺部 <br />\n戴齊口罩面罩 西醫仍中招<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港昨新增63宗確診個案，較前日的85宗有所回落。而在53宗本地個案中，13宗源頭不明，累計確診增至8,301宗。一名55歲男醫生前日確診，他於天水圍俊宏軒商場應診，本月15和18日先後為兩名病人診症，二人為家人，其後確診，該男醫生當時有戴口罩及面罩，惟仍中招。衞生防護中心表示，該診所職員須檢疫，並要求相關求診病人檢測。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：油塘紀律部隊宿舍淪疫廈<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n張表示，天水圍俊宏軒商場的私家醫生吳小春前日確診，編號為8290號，居。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：曾檢測陰性 李偲嫣夫婦無收通知<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lnWDT0pm-C-9W2Lo4oBCNduopJ4=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZSYKN3PC5ZGNPGYHHALV35DOFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlnWDT0pm-C-9W2Lo4oBCNduopJ4%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZSYKN3PC5ZGNPGYHHALV35DOFY.jpg&h=8cc69037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■天水圍一名西醫為確診者應診後，疑除口罩或清潔面罩時感染，診所要關閉14日。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n400病人需轉診所覆診<br />\n<br />\n張竹君指，該醫生在應診時有戴口罩及面罩，可能除下時或清潔時不徹底致感染；其診所職員須檢疫，亦會要求其他相關病人檢測。醫管局總行政經理劉家獻，要求自本月19日起曾去過該診所求醫的人士，以及在本月15及18日與確診者同時間求醫的人士，前往檢測。<br />\n<br />\n劉家獻又指，吳同為醫管。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聯合女病人經篩查確診<br />\n<br />\n另外，聯合醫院一名89歲女病人本月20日因跌倒經急症室入院，入院篩查後確。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，伊利沙伯醫院公佈，第6154號個案、有長期病患的。。。。。。。。。。。。。，現時本港累計有132人因疫症死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mJ8ShrQ4HcFRsQi19CPZBaCSFmE=/1070x740/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WE6QTE6OYFHD3GMVCSMNONUJCM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmJ8ShrQ4HcFRsQi19CPZBaCSFmE%3D%2F1070x740%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWE6QTE6OYFHD3GMVCSMNONUJCM.gif&h=c366b161&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42470e4c29a606e4c96b546bc54c43d2bbd06c81","tid":2337453,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T10:06:29.000Z","msg":"老老實實，我就真係唔信包到實都會中招<br />\n<br />\n係咪有時又係有啲嘢做咗唔講得出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278779578f675b4c800ad1d71c00f1139815d9b3","tid":2337453,"uid":25525,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"42470e4c29a606e4c96b546bc54c43d2bbd06c81","tid":2337453,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T10:06:29.000Z","msg":"老老實實，我就真係唔信包到實都會中招<br />\n<br />\n係咪有時又係有啲嘢做咗唔講得出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T10:09:14.000Z","msg":"包到實但裝備全部感染曬,除同棄置過程都係風險"},{"pid":"80d9325b8ecd93631ad510c5e35615256a850884","tid":2337453,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"42470e4c29a606e4c96b546bc54c43d2bbd06c81","tid":2337453,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T10:06:29.000Z","msg":"老老實實，我就真係唔信包到實都會中招<br />\n<br />\n係咪有時又係有啲嘢做咗唔講得出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T10:11:57.000Z","msg":"個病人除左口罩果陣就有機會噴口水出黎<br />\n留左係台面或者其他地方<br />\n如果唔係每睇完一個病